query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS contestations (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  reservationId INT NOT NULL,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  guideId INT NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('open', 'under_review', 'resolved_user', 'resolved_guide', 'closed') DEFAULT 'open' NOT NULL,
  reason ENUM('expedition_not_completed', 'different_from_description', 'safety_issues', 'guide_no_show', 'poor_service', 'other') NOT NULL,
  description TEXT NOT NULL,
  evidenceUrls JSON,
  guideResponse TEXT,
  guideResponseAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  guideEvidenceUrls JSON,
  resolution TEXT,
  resolvedBy INT,
  resolvedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  refundAmount DECIMAL(10,2),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
